               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370403-name-478" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18370403-name-478" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370403-name-478" type="surname" value="COLEMAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370403-name-478" type="given" value="JAMES BUTT"></interp>JAMES BUTT COLEMAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a cheesemonger, and live in Ironmonger-row, 8t Luke's. On the 8th of March, I received information, and missed a piece of bacon—I saw the prisoner running—I pursued, and cried "Stop thief"—he was met by the policeman, who took him—he gave me the bacon.</p>
